<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5"> صحيح بلفظ:</span> <span class="c2">((عملاً)</span>) مكان: <span class="c2">((توبة)</span>) ـ <span class="c2">((الصحيحة)</span>) <span class="c2">(٣٦٩)</span> , <span class="c2">((الإرواء)</span>) <span class="c2">(٥/ ٣٢)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
